  "description": "<h4>Application</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Nissan S13 240SX Silvia 1989-1994</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Package Includes</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Front coilovers × 2 pcs</li>\n<li>Rear coilovers × 2 pcs</li>\n<li>Wrench × 2 pcs</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Features</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Mono-tube shock design provides larger oil and gas capacity</li>\n<li>Adjustable ride height</li>\n<li>Adjustable pre-load spring tension</li>\n<li>High-tensile performance springs tested over 600,000 cycles with less than 0.04% distortion</li>\n<li>Special surface treatment enhances durability and performance</li>\n<li>Includes fitted rubber boots to protect dampers</li>\n<li>Improved handling without compromising ride comfort</li>\n<li>Affordable appearance upgrade</li>\n<li>Easy installation with proper tools</li>\n<li>Ideal for track, drift, performance road use and daily driving</li>\n<li>All accessories shown in photos included</li>\n<li>Default 1-year warranty for any manufacturing defect, upgrade to 2 years with our Extended Warranty Program</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Technical Specifications</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Spring rate Front: 8 kg/mm</li>\n<li>Spring rate Rear: 6 kg/mm</li>\n<li>Adjustable height: Yes</li>\n<li>Adjustable camber plate: Front only</li>\n<li>Adjustable damper: Non-adjustable</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Warranty</h4>\n<p>All products include a 1-year warranty from purchase date. Please provide proof of purchase (order number preferred) for warranty claims. To expedite claims, include detailed images/videos of the issue. Defective items typically don't need to be returned. Additional information may be requested for proper diagnosis and resolution.</p>",
